{"tid":711472,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［半飲食半學術？］帶飯難題","createTime":"2018-06-21T14:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T11:54:35.000Z","uid":190923,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"9bd9224f83731ae0814c8d01e159a2d2f985be07","tid":711472,"uid":190923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:22:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我岩岩開始番工 <br />\n冇錢到一個幾嚴峻幾狀況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想儲錢的話我諗帶飯係不二之選 <br />\n唔好意思 問題終於黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我朝早要十點起身 夜晚九點半先番到屋企<br />\n屋企係無飯家庭 留飯餸係冇可能<br />\n（平時自己煮野食 蒜頭都要自己買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n但我呢啲時間放工係買唔到餸 <br />\n以下係我得出既解決辦法：<br />\n一  8點起身落街市買送 整下一日既飯<br />\n （因為要凍既狀態帶飯 冇得當日整當日食 會臭）<br />\n<del> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">唔知係咪</span></del><br />\n二  買7仔/OK啲飯番去叮<br />\n （求推介邊隻飯唔伏）<br />\n三 夜晚番樓下街市買兩餸飯($35) 番屋企分開聽日食果餐放雪櫃 第二日就可以輕鬆帶<br />\n （但會好少選擇 因為果間野我黎黎去去正係食佢果幾味餸）<br />\n四 唔撚食/食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求各種專業意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5950f3c56268c33dba42c3a09fde40042ecaf745","tid":711472,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:24:46.000Z","msg":"生叮雞"},{"pid":"26f5d9bf8ae35c532b85d0557944971ca87bfd50","tid":711472,"uid":178110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:27:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d4ed46a591af6dc4c807f0a7da5c3f3da6c9728","tid":711472,"uid":190923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"26f5d9bf8ae35c532b85d0557944971ca87bfd50","tid":711472,"uid":178110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:27:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:28:41.000Z","msg":"九龍塘"},{"pid":"8e5be9c524121357aa4604c94f9dcab46f24fc9c","tid":711472,"uid":190923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5950f3c56268c33dba42c3a09fde40042ecaf745","tid":711472,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:24:46.000Z","msg":"生叮雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:30:40.000Z","msg":"我應該買唔起一隻雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54652461264f05dbef19c2b102e0ca7cda578eb1","tid":711472,"uid":72581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:30:52.000Z","msg":"參考下d日式飯盒，多數都係凍嘅<br />\n或者整沙律三文治"},{"pid":"66e54806c90ccb7cb49a7288b3e58d8d4cedd21e","tid":711472,"uid":190923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:32:34.000Z","msg":"岩岩番屋企 連賣帶飯果啲玻璃兜既雜貨舖都關哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed396612f0ca2a1f44fa88346ec333b60a6763b3","tid":711472,"uid":96,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:32:51.000Z","msg":"煮意粉會唔會ok<br />\n啲醬又平又現成 仲唔會難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0cf92eb2117adda272bbb4fdb147b54dfc908e","tid":711472,"uid":179120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:32:59.000Z","msg":"7仔肉醬意粉，窮撚救星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c51115e14691ef37c27246bd2b083099d28c99","tid":711472,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:34:14.000Z","msg":"sushi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031ed099eec34adc329544301f59b25a0fe5aac6","tid":711472,"uid":44890,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:36:49.000Z","msg":"咩工種先？<br />\n<br />\n如果office嘅 <br />\n好多選擇啦 五花八門咁濟<br />\n<br />\n拎少少本買啲蒸煮二合一嘅電子煲<br />\n<br />\n去惠康百佳買啲冰鮮菜 + 米粉又一餐<br />\n<br />\n得閒咪蒸下糯米雞/點心 + 麵包 又一餐<br />\n<br />\n蒸燒賣 腸粉又得 <br />\n<br />\n你咁嘅返放工時間<br />\n<br />\n邊個話即日唔帶得？"},{"pid":"1d3e2b706ac0854db07511e86d34cab05ab70f9b","tid":711472,"uid":190923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime