018-06-22T08:50:04.000Z","msg":"係囉, 有無咁誇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c791d9da7f99e579c294f12da0349d6e0dfe99a4","tid":711472,"uid":121409,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:58:38.000Z","msg":"唔介意唔新鮮同唔健康可以星期六日買餸，dum入冰箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n星期日煲一大煲飯分七份，dum入冰箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再煮定兩三日份量ge餸，dum<span style=\"font-size: large;\">入</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冰</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">箱</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976b29dfe4a27c1f84b1db3a930c9a25b3d0fbe4","tid":711472,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T12:47:15.000Z","msg":"睇下外國meal prep <br />\n可能啱你<br />\n佢地雪雪櫃都得"},{"pid":"d030c2284bb02cbb0d36d78f4508949cc3a150fc","tid":711472,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T13:22:46.000Z","msg":"每月1500蚊<br />\n當你返22日工<br />\n每日可以食68蚊嘅餐<br />\n<br />\n你仲要冇得食屋企<br />\n要自己買餸自己煮<br />\n一個月慳唔慳到1000蚊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2a564006ef07610ea29018833df99b72c53270","tid":711472,"uid":120093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccf0e44b25744abf088a26b75464be7b83c13d22","tid":711472,"uid":190923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:49:00.000Z","msg":"感恩各位既專業意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾驚有人又話帶飯寒暄 窮撚<br />\n但食麵包果刻聞到同事啲帶飯咪真係覺得好撚陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:52:28.000Z","msg":"整三文治囉 飽肚又健康 你女仔一句減肥ko人啦"},{"pid":"1ebff0e34e4dd1f618532b2044d445fdb90389fb","tid":711472,"uid":100912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:06:09.000Z","msg":"即日朝早煮入玻璃盒<br />\n返公司放入雪櫃，食晏再叮一定得<br />\n成日都係咁帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD菜仲唔會黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a461485d07dcae4d7608b9cfa3001064a85d1fa","tid":711472,"uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:43:31.000Z","msg":"有啲方法可以即煮即食<br />\n12蚊店或者生活用品店有種烚粉dull<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你放包意粉或者通粉係公司<br />\nlunch時用烚粉dull加熱水再放入微波爐叮熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n759, jusco 12蚊店有堆一包包咖哩醬，意粉醬<br />\n再買樽雜錦香草同即磨黑椒放公司<br />\n烚好意粉倒入飯盒倒入以上醬料及香料調味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想要d菜就星期六日或得閒時買定<br />\n早上返工前烚左佢放餐盒<br />\n<br />\nching點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf234bec4fd89f7c13515fa05c864f653be9248","tid":711472,"uid":178110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T00:08:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a38002dd2a14ad987478893c420ec0070769f19","tid":711472,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T00:13:07.000Z","msg":"整一大煲咖哩 擺雪櫃 夠食成個星期<br />\n咖哩雜菜、薯仔、黃豆<br />\n肉就唔好放了 會臭"},{"pid":"b7d6dfbb1f52f9d2795c742dbe43f0980c222a5f","tid":711472,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T00:14:02.000Z","msg":"食嫌咖哩就轉整白汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b5ddad7f5736d0bf65a116cef613196fd3f4d4","tid":711472,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T00:14:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食<em><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>厭</strong></span></em>咖哩就轉整白汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"066570121ce90d2cf9c686a8fe8ee0b65b968827","tid":711472,"uid":178110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:41:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除